<h1>Welcome to Mario's Market!</h1>

<p>For over 30 years, Mario's has been a proud member of the Tri-state area community! In addition to serving <a href="https://pangtodd.github.io/PizzaParlor/">the best Pizza</a> in the area, we are also the go-to spot for hard-to-find items! Please view our products below, and feel free to leave a review.</p>

<% if @products.any? %>

  <h3>Spotlight! our most reviewed product:
    <% @products.most_reviews.each do |product| %>
      <%= link_to product.name, product_path(product) %></h3>
    <% end %>
  
  <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1">
    new additions
  </button>

  <div class="collapse" id="collapse1">
    <ul>
      <% @products.three_most_recent.each do |product| %>
        <li><%= link_to product.name, product_path(product) %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <br>
  <br>
  <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
    Proudly made in the USA!
  </button>
  <div class="collapse" id="collapse2">
    <ul>
      <% @products.from_usa.each do |product| %>
        <li><%= link_to product.name, product_path(product) %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <br>
  <br>
  <a class = "btn btn-primary" href='/products' role="button">All products</a>

<% else %>
  <p>Hold your horses, we're still stocking the shelves!</p>
<% end %>
<br>
<br>
 <a class = "btn btn-primary" href='/products/new' role="button">Enter new product</a>